0.8: Initial public release.  Alpha state.  Comprehensive documentation not
completed.  Hopefully public feedback helps improve documentation and maybe
design.

0.9: Beta state.  Comprehensive documentation and source comments completed.
INDEX files in each directory that succinctly explain files of directories.
Hopefully public feedback helps notice and improve design flaws.

0.9.x: Any design changes before stabilizing for 1.x series.

1.0: First stable release.  1.x series will maintain stable API for public's
long-term use.

1.x: Any improvements or enhancements that do not affect stability of 1.x API.
